@startuml
' --- whole-map provenance: cycle that introduced each @id ---
' @cycle(SEQ-ARCH-TRACK, 0028)
' @id(SEQ-ARCH-TRACK)
' @ref(USE-TRACK-ARCH)
' @desc(SEQ-ARCH-TRACK, "Implemented as the workflow documented in .mdd/docs/architecture-tracking.md (shipped by mdd init): read the how-to; update the relevant .mdd/architecture/*.yml; for a decision APPEND a new entry and mark the prior one superseded (superseded_by) rather than rewriting; keep components.yml in sync with the component diagrams; commit (git is the interim structured-diff history; a structured mdd arch diff/status verb is the planned follow-up).")
' Current-side sequence for tracking an architectural change (cycle 0028).
title Tracking an architectural change (current)

actor "Agent" as Agent
participant ".mdd/docs/architecture-tracking.md" as Doc
participant ".mdd/architecture/*.yml" as Spec
participant "git" as Git

Agent -> Doc : read the tracking workflow
Agent -> Spec : update components / constraints
alt a decision changes
  Agent -> Spec : append new Decision; mark prior superseded
end
Agent -> Git : commit (structured diff is the interim history)
note right of Git: a structured `mdd arch diff` / `status` verb is a follow-up
@enduml
